{"tid":1427330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣】浸大學生會會長藏攻擊性武器真相","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:01:41.000Z","uid":254898,"like":116,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"522ee036f0dd3d8c528d0ef389d2b979420f3b5b","tid":1427330,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"而家tvb同班狗成日係度鐳射槍 鐳射槍咁<br />\n槍你老母，真係好容易誤導到班人。<br />\n岩岩睇到有youtuber澄清好好，<br />\n引用一下。改翻做口語方便宣傳，<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/comingho/community\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fcomingho%2Fcommunity&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=c029cb3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/comingho/community</a><br />\n詳細都可以去佢度睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Reu5oJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FReu5oJg.jpg&h=d4adbcd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1. 呢個叫觀星筆，唔係所謂既「鐳射槍」<br />\n一般與一枝筆長度相若(10~20cm)<br />\n鐳射輸出功率介乎5~20毫瓦<br />\n(參考：上課用鐳射筆 1~5毫瓦)<br />\n係兩人或以上既群體觀星活動時<br />\n主要用途係用作觀測位置指示<br />\n例如想集中觀看 英仙座M76<br />\n就會用觀星筆照過去<br />\n大家就會好清楚觀察方向<br />\n(如果呢個都叫槍 咁鉛筆係唔係都要改叫鉛槍? )<br />\n2. 而家正值大學各學生會的迎新營活動時間<br />\n作為有做過大學學生會幹事既我<br />\n我可以同大家講<br />\n有時候活動在截止之前<br />\n會突然有好多人報名參加 (比預期多)<br />\n所以也有可能需要臨時添加物資<br />\n假如琴晚先為活動添加物資  都係合理既(僅僅10支咋喔)<br />\n3. 琴日浸大學生會會長係購買觀星筆時<br />\n係冇使用過的情況下<br />\n警察就以「持有攻擊性武器」拘捕<br />\n咁日常學生所帶的剪刀、直尺等<br />\n甚至環保人士自備餐具：叉子、不鏽鋼吸管等<br />\n都有構成傷亡風險<br />\n那係唔係都通通抓回警察局?<br />\n4. 有部分報導話鐳射槍功率可以達5000毫瓦<br />\n(以此渲染事件既嚴重性，實際觀星筆只有鐳射輸出功率介乎5~20毫瓦)<br />\n假如係真既<br />\n要拘捕既唔應該係售賣的人咩?<br />\n更何況係香港原本就冇法例管制<br />\n市面所出售的鐳射筆規格。<br />\n<br />\n憑咩冇做出任何犯罪行為<br />\n只要懷疑你 就可以拘捕你<br />\n呢個就係大家當初都反送中既原因。"},{"pid":"2a98eda014e41cb2fca526befb5e5a26c80517f8","tid":1427330,"uid":254898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"幫下手推下，唔好搞到大眾被誤導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd86a1c369eeecc071e2d8737bea926a687ab06","tid":1427330,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c3b273c342bca094c9c6ce08fb0cbec8b05fa9f","tid":1427330,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fd86a1c369eeecc071e2d8737bea926a687ab06","tid":1427330,"uid":172797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dcc0e7b3bb3d508b8bf94b665977ef51b9a9b5","tid":1427330,"uid":281787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:59:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5057b51fcd6dc237ca99cedd3814137ad8df8243","tid":1427330,"uid":254872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"help push"},{"pid":"2b86b39a006ee25868799ab8024fc94ded620301","tid":1427330,"uid":298893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"除非佢果10支, 係戰艦級別的鐳射槍, 一擊可以將25MM既裝甲輕易擊穿, 我就信佢係攻擊性武器喇.<br />\n<br />\n建議今日去垃圾警犬記者會的記者一人帶10支出席兼開動,  睇下佢會唔會CALL齊人拉晒佢地"},{"pid":"b8a4c0d239208248e2e790fcee68c6844c01826d","tid":1427330,"uid":273252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"522ee036f0dd3d8c528d0ef389d2b979420f3b5b","tid":1427330,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"而家tvb同班狗成日係度鐳射槍 鐳射槍咁<br />\n槍你老母，真係好容易誤導到班人。<br />\n岩岩睇到有youtuber澄清好好，<br />\n引用一下。改翻做口語方便宣傳，<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/comingho/community\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fcomingho%2Fcommunity&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=c029cb3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/comingho/community</a><br />\n詳細都可以去佢度睇<br />\n<img src=\"https